---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---

<SiteLayout title="About — Mehrdad Abdolghafari" description="About Mehrdad Abdolghafari — Principal Cloud Engineer, Microsoft MVP, Azure & Kubernetes platform lead at RBC">
	<div class="page-header">
		<h1>About Me</h1>
	</div>

	<div class="about-content">
		<div class="badges">
			<span class="badge mvp">🏆 Microsoft MVP — Azure</span>
			<span class="badge ignite">🎤 Microsoft Ignite Speaker</span>
			<span class="badge role">☁️ Principal Cloud Engineer</span>
		</div>

		<p>
			I'm Mehrdad Abdolghafari — Principal Cloud Engineer at <strong>Royal Bank of Canada (RBC)</strong>,
			where I lead the Azure, AI and Kubernetes platforms. I'm a <strong>Microsoft MVP</strong> in Azure
			and a speaker at <strong>Microsoft Ignite</strong>.
		</p>

		<h2>What I Do at RBC</h2>
		<p>
			I lead the design and engineering of the Azure Kubernetes Platform at RBC, ensuring secure
			and smart infrastructure for hundreds of application teams. I drive the design and operation
			of large-scale, secure, and compliant Azure and Kubernetes environments with a focus on
			automation, GitOps, and platform reliability to enable developer self-service and innovation
			at enterprise scale.
		</p>
		<p>
			My background in cloud, Kubernetes and software engineering empowered me to lead the
			world-class Azure and AKS infrastructure in RBC — leveraging a mix of Azure and Kubernetes
			concepts and best practices in self-service solutions at enterprise scale.
		</p>

		<h2>Speaking & Community</h2>
		<p>
			I presented at <strong>Microsoft Ignite</strong> on
			<em>"Fast and flexible inference on open-source AI models at scale"</em> — covering how to run
			open-source AI models from local environments to cloud deployments using Azure Container Apps,
			serverless GPUs, and AKS for scalable, high-performance LLM operations.
		</p>
		<p>
			I played a pivotal role in helping RBC become <strong>#1 in Canada and top 3 globally</strong> in
			AI maturity among banks.
		</p>

		<h2>Focus Areas</h2>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Agentic AI</strong> — Designing autonomous AI systems, LLM inference at scale, and AI platform architecture</li>
			<li><strong>Cloud Platform</strong> — Azure architecture, cloud-native solutions, hybrid infrastructure, and platform engineering</li>
			<li><strong>Kubernetes</strong> — AKS at enterprise scale, GitOps, operator patterns, GPU scheduling, and developer self-service</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Patent</h2>
		<div class="patent-card">
			<div class="patent-icon">📜</div>
			<div class="patent-info">
				<div class="patent-number">US Patent 12,494,993</div>
				<h3 class="patent-title">Multicloud Hosting for Containerized Applications</h3>
				<p class="patent-abstract">
					A method and system for deploying containerized applications from a central
					application management hub to multiple cloud environments simultaneously,
					using a unified control plane with routing tables, operator services, and
					GitOps-based deployment across Azure, AWS, and OpenShift clusters.
				</p>
				<div class="patent-meta">
					<span>Filed: Sep 2, 2022</span>
					<span>Granted: Dec 9, 2025</span>
					<span>Assignee: Royal Bank of Canada</span>
				</div>
				<div class="patent-inventors">
					Co-inventors: Vinh Tran, Edmund Lau, Mehrdad Abdolghafari, Michael Jastrzebski, Ranji Narine
				</div>
				<a href="https://patents.justia.com/patent/12494993" target="_blank" class="patent-link">View Patent →</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2>Technology Focus</h2>
		<p>
			Azure Kubernetes and Open Source — with roles spanning Developer, Researcher, Trainer, and Content Creator.
		</p>

		<div class="connect">
			<h2>Connect</h2>
			<div class="connect-links">
				<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mehrdad-abdolghafari-26052656" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
				<a href="https://mvp.microsoft.com/en-US/mvp/profile/f4415dd9-1b2b-4eb5-8953-2955f32a80f3" target="_blank">Microsoft MVP Profile</a>
				<a href="https://ignite.microsoft.com/en-US/speakers/db511280-f85d-5d4c-2610-6bfcaa462a17" target="_blank">Microsoft Ignite</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/mehrdadsilver" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</SiteLayout>

<style>
	.about-content {
		max-width: 720px;
	}
	.badges {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.6rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.badge {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.4rem;
